Summary: UFO sighting in Julian CA - outside san diego
divs: Sighting DetailsLast night my girlfriend and I went out to our backyard in Julian, Ca to look at the stars as it was a really clear and beautiful night. As we looked up at the starts we noticed one of the stars moving across the sky at a very hight rate of speed. It looked like all the other stars, the same size and color except it was moving across the sky very fast, we watched it for about 2-3 minutes until it disappeared. It definately was not a shooting star. I was wondering if anyone else reported seeing it or if Julian has alot of sightings in general?
